Key Match Events: Evan Mobley finished with 21 points, 10 rebounds, and seven assists, while Jarrett Allen finished with 25 points, 12 rebounds, and six assists.
Post-Match Reflections: Evan Mobley said, 'Yeah, definitely starting to feel like that' when asked if he feels like a star player.
Jarrett Allen said, 'They finally learned who Evan Mobley is and they still have a lot more to learn.'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Cavs and Thunder matchup was the game of the night, as both teams came into the contest with long winning streaks.
The Cavs are playing some of the best basketball in the league this season.
Others: Darius Garland made an All-Star pitch for himself and his teammates.
The coach wasn't mentioned, but it was mentioned that the Cavs coach Kenny Atkinson had a message before the pivotal Thunder matchup.
